SQL_STMT_U.val: select CREM_ADMNO, CREM_CLNTNO, min(CREM_TYPE), cast(sum(CMON_CURRBALINVESTMENT) as decimal(13,2)), min(a.CLNT110_NAME1), min(a.CLNT804_RISKRATING), min(a.CLNT209_CONTRACT_END), min(a.CLNT807_DATELASTSUMMARY), min(a.CLNT807_POSTPONEDATESUMMARY), min(a.CLNT204_EMP_COMM), min(a.CLNT205_EMP_CONTACT) from :1/CREM cross join :1/CLNT a cross join :1/ADMN join :1/CLNT b on b.CLNT103_COMM_ADMNO = a.CLNT103_COMM_ADMNO and b.CLNT103_COMM_CLNTNO = a.CLNT103_COMM_CLNTNO or b.CLNT104_LEGAL_ADMNO = a.CLNT104_LEGAL_ADMNO and b.CLNT104_LEGAL_CLNTNO = a.CLNT104_LEGAL_CLNTNO left outer join :1/CMON on CMON_ADMNO = b.CLNT101_ADMNO and CMON_CLNTNO = b.CLNT102_CLNTNO and CMON_YEAR = :3 and CMON_MONTH = :4 and CMON_CURRENCY = ADMN_CURRENCY where a.CLNT101_ADMNO = ADMN_NO and CREM_TYPE = :2 and a.CLNT101_ADMNO = CREM_ADMNO and a.CLNT102_CLNTNO = CREM_CLNTNO :5 group by CREM_ADMNO, CREM_CLNTNO order by CREM_ADMNO, CREM_CLNTNO for fetch only
